{
  "id": "13-2",
  "title": "Act 2: {{characters.elias.name}}'s Intervention",
  "startNode": "main",
  "nodes": {
    "main": {
      "events": [
        {
          "type": "marker",
          "id": "ch13_act2_start"
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "blackout",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeIn",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.soren.name}} accessed the neural network on the fifth night.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.elias.name}} felt it. A faint sensation of another neural connection node activating in the same space. He plugged into his own port almost in the same second and followed.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "scanlines",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The world inside the neural network was dark. Not the darkness of physics, but the emptiness unique to sparse data spaces. But {{characters.soren.name}}'s node was like a bright light. {{characters.elias.name}} locked onto his position the moment he entered.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "That node was advancing at a speed {{characters.elias.name}} had never seen before, like a chisel, chewing through the Ark's core system defenses layer by layer.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.elias.name}}",
          "text": "{{characters.soren.name}}. Stop.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.soren.name}}",
          "text": "{{characters.elias.name}}. Don't block me.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.elias.name}}",
          "text": "I'm going to. You knew I would, so you waited until I was asleep to access this. But I didn't sleep, so I'm here now. Stop. Let's talk.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.soren.name}}",
          "text": "We talked yesterday. I haven't changed.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.elias.name}} revoked {{characters.soren.name}}'s encryption token, cutting off his access path to the central network.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.elias.name}}",
          "text": "To get past me, you have to go through me.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.soren.name}}'s identity in this network was only one of many. He pulled out a small black box and pressed the activation button.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "glitch",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.elias.name}} suddenly felt a wave of vertigo, his vision snapping back to the local neural network. A firewall. {{characters.soren.name}} had locked out his internet privileges.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.soren.name}} continued pushing toward the Ark core. {{characters.elias.name}} tried to catch up and intercede again, but felt his node locked down by a counter-measure. That lock's boundary was calibrated precisely—below the threshold of what he could move. Not to hurt him. Just to make it impossible for him to continue interfering.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.soren.name}}",
          "text": "I don't want to hurt you. <delay ms=\"400\"/>When I'm done, we'll both be free.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.elias.name}}",
          "text": "{{characters.soren.name}}——",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.soren.name}}",
          "text": "{{characters.elias.name}}. <delay ms=\"300\"/>I've calculated it for {{characters.alea.name}}. If that system hadn't existed, she wouldn't have died here, wouldn't have scattered in some unknown corner of the Wasteland. She didn't deserve that ending. I'm settling the debt.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.elias.name}} said nothing. He was locked in place at that node, watching {{characters.soren.name}}'s light continue deeper, farther, until it vanished into the darkness of data.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 12
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 2000
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "scanlines",
          "args": {
            "enabled": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeOut",
          "ms": 1500,
          "args": {
            "stay": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "end"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "onComplete": [
    "complete"
  ]
}